prod.full_name: Jordan 1 Low Reverse Bred Pebbled Swoosh
prod.desciption:
The Jordan 1 Low Reverse Bred has the same legendary durability and functionality features of Michael Jordan's first signature sneaker but with a low-cut design. They come with a unique and robust construction that makes them perfect for the office or the court.

The Jordan 1 Low Reverse Bred features a white Air midsole, ideal for both the court and the street. It also arrives with Swoosh logos that run across the sides, while the wings and Jumpman logo are featured at the heel and tongue, respectively. The side panels and toe come with black micro-perforated leather, while red leather covers the overlays. Padding at the ankle enhances the shoe's functionality and comfort.

The Jordan 1 Low Reverse Bred was released in September of 2020 for $90.
